%N A396110 Number of digraphs on n labeled nodes such that every node is reachable from node 1.
%C A396110 Number of control-flow graphs (single-entry digraphs) on n labeled basic blocks, self-loops disallowed; multiply by 2^n to allow them.
%C A396110 Equivalently, initially connected digraphs with a fixed source: Robinson's I~(n) intermediate in the derivation of A003030/A003028.
%C A396110 A003028(n) counts the same objects with an unspecified source.
%F A396110 a(n) = 2^(n*(n-1)) - Sum_{k=1..n-1} binomial(n-1,k-1) * a(k) * 2^((n-k)*(n-1)); the sum is empty at n = 1, giving a(1) = 1.
%Y A396110 Cf. A003028, A003030, A350360, A351052 (unlabeled analog).
%K A396110 nonn,new
%O A396110 1,2
%A A396110 _Gregory Morse_, Jul 13 2026
